What you need to know:

The youth team, dubbed “Rising Stars”, will depart for Tanzania on Saturday to compete in the Cecafa Under-20 ChampionshipsThis nine-team tournament will be staged at the Black Rhino Academy and Sheikh Amri Abeid stadium in Arusha between November 22 and December 2Kenya, coached by Stanley Okumbi, are in a tough-looking Pool 'C' at the tournament with matches against Ethiopia and Sudan lined up